lla%3A+squad%C2%A0sheets\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/email.png\" border=\"0\" /></a></td></tr></table></div><br/><br/><a href=\"http://da.feedsportal.com/r/163644759672/u/49/f/639039/c/34708/s/2aeb11cd/a2.htm\"><img src=\"http://da.feedsportal.com/r/163644759672/u/49/f/639039/c/34708/s/2aeb11cd/a2.img\" border=\"0\"/></a><img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://pi.feedsportal.com/r/163644759672/u/49/f/639039/c/34708/s/2aeb11cd/a2t.img\" border=\"0\"/><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/theguardian/football/rss/~4/zP8vk5TwdwY\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\"/>" "http://feeds.guardian.co.uk/~r/theguardian/football/rss/~3/zP8vk5TwdwY/manchester-united-aston-villa-squad-sheets" (20849 20124) old 19 nil nil ((title nil "Manchester United v Aston Villa: squad sheets") (link nil "http://feeds.guardian.co.uk/~r/theguardian/football/rss/~3/zP8vk5TwdwY/manchester-united-aston-villa-squad-sheets") (description nil "<div class=\"track\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://hits.guardian.co.uk/b/ss/guardiangu-feeds/1/H.25.4/96759?ns=guardian&pageName=Article%3Amanchester-united-aston-villa-squad-sheets%3A1896494&ch=Football&c3=Guardian&c4=Manchester+United+%28Football%29%2CAston+Villa+%28Football%29%2CPremier+League+%28Football%29%2CFootball%2CSport&c5=Premier+League&c6=&c7=2013%2F04%2F19+03%3A03&c8=1896494&c9=Article&c10=News&c13=Squad+sheets+%28football%29&c19=GUK&c47=UK&c64=UK&c65=Manchester+United+v+Aston+Villa%3A+squad%26nbsp%3Bsheets&c66=Sport&c72=&c73=&c74=&c75=&h2=GU%2FSport%2FFootball%2FManchester+United\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" /></div><p>If Manchester City lose at Tottenham on Sunday afternoon, Manchester United's 20th championship will be confirmed with three points against 17th-placed Aston Villa. Whatever occurs at White Hart Lane, Sir Alex Ferguson has informed his players the aim is to win all of their final five matches so Paul Lambert's side can expect a difficult evening at Old Trafford. When United's team sheet is issued all eyes will search for Wayne Rooney after he was replaced at West Ham during the week due to a disappointing display in the 2-2 draw. <strong>Jamie&nbsp;Jackson</strong></p><p><strong>Venue</strong> Old Trafford, Monday 8pm</p><p><strong>Tickets </strong>£30-52 (0161 868 8000)</p><p><strong>Last season </strong>Man Utd 4 Aston Villa 0</p><p><strong>Referee </strong>Anthony Taylor</p><p><strong>This season's matches</strong> 22 <strong>Y</strong>53, <strong>R</strong>6, 2.68 cards per game</p><p><strong>Odds </strong>Man Utd 1-4 Aston Villa 11-1 Draw 11-2</p><h2><strong>Manchester United</strong></h2><p><strong>Subs from</strong> Lindegaard, Evans, Buttner, Powell, Anderson, Giggs, Smalling, Nani, Welbeck, Hernández, Jones</p><p><strong>Doubtful</strong> None</p><p><strong>Injured</strong> Scholes (knee, 5 May), Fletcher (bowel, Aug), Young (ankle, Aug)</p><p><strong>Suspended</strong> None</p><p><strong>Form guide</strong> DWLWWW</p><p><strong>Disciplinary record</strong> Y48 R0</p><p><strong>Leading scorer</strong> Van&nbsp;Persie 21</p><h2><strong>Aston Villa</strong></h2><p><strong>Subs from</strong> Given, Dawkins, Sylla, Bannan, Bowery, Holman, Lichaj, El&nbsp;Ahmadi, Burke, Stevens, Carruthers, Ireland, Clark</p><p><strong>Doubtful</strong> None</p><p><strong>Injured</strong> Gardner (knee, Aug), Herd (foot, Aug), Albrighton (foot, unknown), Dunne (groin, unknown), Petrov (leukaemia, unknown)</p><p><strong>Suspended</strong> None</p><p><strong>Form guide</strong> DWLWWL</p><p><strong>Disciplinary record</strong> Y68 R2</p><p><strong>Leading scorer</strong> Benteke 15</p><h2><strong>Match pointers</strong></h2><p><strong>• Villa have won just one of their past 34 visits to United in the Premier League – 1-0 in December 2009 with Gabriel Agbonlahor getting the goal</strong></p><p></p><p><strong>• Agbonlahor needs one more goal to pass Dwight Yorke (60) as Villa's all-time Premier League top scorer</strong></p><p></p><p><strong>• United have scored in each of their past 21 top-flight games, the next longest run this season is five (by Chelsea and Villa)</strong></p><p></p><p><strong>• Bradley Guzan has made more saves (205) than any other keeper in the division</strong></p><p></p><p><strong>• Shinji Kagawa has been involved in five goals (three scored, two assisted) in his past seven appearances</strong></p><div class=\"related\" style=\"float: left; margin-right: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px;\"><ul><li><a href=\"http://www.guardian.co.uk/football/manchester-united\">Manchester United</a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.guardian.co.uk/football/aston-villa\">Aston Villa</a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.guardian.co.uk/football/premierleague\">Premier League</a></li></ul></div><br/><div class=\"terms\"><a href=\"http://www.guardian.co.uk\">guardian.co.uk</a> &copy; 2013 Guardian News and Media Limited or its affiliated companies. All rights reserved. | Use of this content is subject to our <a href=\"http://www.guardian.co.uk/help/terms-of-service\">Terms & Conditions</a> | <a href=\"http://www.guardian.co.uk/help/feeds\">More Feeds</a></div><p style=\"clear:both\" /><img width='1' height='1' src='http://guardian.co.uk.feedsportal.com/c/34708/f/639039/s/2aeb11cd/mf.gif' border='0'/><div class='mf-viral'><table border='0'><tr><td valign='middle'><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.guardian.co.uk%2Ffootball%2F2013%2Fapr%2F19%2Fmanchester-united-aston-villa-squad-sheets&t=Manchester+United+v+Aston+Villa%3A+squad%C2%A0sheets\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" border=\"0\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.guardian.co.uk%2Ffootball%2F2013%2Fapr%2F19%2Fmanchester-united-aston-villa-squad-sheets&t=Manchester+United+v+Aston+Villa%3A+squad%C2%A0sheets\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" border=\"0\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=htt