ootball/2013/apr/19/liverpool-chelsea-squad-sheets") (dc:creator nil) (dc:subject nil "Football") (dc:date nil "2013-04-19T15:17:38Z") (dc:type nil "Article") (dc:identifier nil "407525760") (media:keywords nil "Liverpool, Chelsea, Premier League, Football, Sport") (media:content ((height . "650") (lang . " ") (type . "image/jpeg") (width . "460") (url . "http://static.guim.co.uk/sys-images/Sport/Pix/pictures/2013/4/19/1366383911897/Liverpool-v-Chelsea-001.jpg")) (media:credit ((scheme . "urn:ebu")) "Graphic") (media:description nil "Liverpool v Chelsea: Probable starters in bold, contenders in light. Illustration: Graphic")) (feedburner:origLink nil "http://www.guardian.co.uk/football/2013/apr/19/liverpool-chelsea-squad-sheets"))) ("Fulham v Arsenal: squad sheets" "<div class=\"track\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://hits.guardian.co.uk/b/ss/guardiangu-feeds/1/H.25.4/52413?ns=guardian&pageName=Article%3Afulham-arsenal-squad-sheets%3A1896566&ch=Football&c3=Guardian&c4=Fulham+%28Football%29%2CArsenal+FC+%28Football%29%2CPremier+League+%28Football%29%2CFootball%2CSport&c5=Europa+League%2CPremier+League&c6=&c7=2013%2F04%2F19+03%3A59&c8=1896566&c9=Article&c10=News&c13=Squad+sheets+%28football%29&c19=GUK&c47=UK&c64=UK&c65=Fulham+v+Arsenal%3A+squad%26nbsp%3Bsheets&c66=Sport&c72=&c73=&c74=&c75=&h2=GU%2FSport%2FFootball%2FFulham\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" /></div><p>This could be a pivotal weekend for those involved in the chase for Champions League qualifying places with Tottenham hosting Manchester City on Sunday while, on Saturday, Arsenal face a Fulham side who have failed to win any of their last three matches. Triumph at Craven Cottage and Arsène Wenger's men could move five points clear of Spurs in third, albeit having played a game more. The visitors should at least fancy their chances of scoring against a team who conceded three goals against Chelsea in midweek. <strong>Sachin Nakrani</strong></p><p><strong>Venue</strong> Craven Cottage, Saturday 3pm</p><p><strong>Ticke