//www.guardian.co.uk/football/2013/apr/19/fulham-arsenal-squad-sheets") (dc:creator nil) (dc:subject nil "Football") (dc:date nil "2013-04-19T14:59:25Z") (dc:type nil "Article") (dc:identifier nil "407525316") (media:keywords nil "Fulham, Arsenal, Premier League, Football, Sport") (media:content ((height . "650") (lang . " ") (type . "image/jpeg") (width . "460") (url . "http://static.guim.co.uk/sys-images/Sport/Pix/pictures/2013/4/19/1366383436421/Fulham-v-Arsenal-001.jpg")) (media:credit ((scheme . "urn:ebu")) "Graphic") (media:description nil "Fulham v Arsenal: Probable starters in bold, contenders in light. Illustration: Graphic")) (feedburner:origLink nil "http://www.guardian.co.uk/football/2013/apr/19/fulham-arsenal-squad-sheets"))) ("Queens Park Rangers v Stoke City: squad sheets" "<div class=\"track\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://hits.guardian.co.uk/b/ss/guardiangu-feeds/1/H.25.4/94463?ns=guardian&pageName=Article%3Aqpr-stoke-city-squad-sheets%3A1896558&ch=Football&c3=Guardian&c4=QPR+%28Football%29%2CStoke+City+%28Football%29%2CPremier+League+%28Football%29%2CFootball%2CSport&c5=Premier+League&c6=&c7=2013%2F04%2F19+03%3A53&c8=1896558&c9=Article&c10=News&c13=Squad+sheets+%28football%29&c19=GUK&c47=UK&c64=UK&c65=Queens+Park+Rangers+v+Stoke+City%3A+squad%26nbsp%3Bsheets&c66=Sport&c72=&c73=&c74=&c75=&h2=GU%2FSport%2FFootball%2FQPR\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" /></div><p>Stoke's victory over Liverpool on Boxing Day left the Potters in eighth place, three points ahead of Brendan Rodgers' team and two behind Arsenal. But since that win at the Britannia Tony Pulis's side have picked up only six points from 14 matches, the fewest in the Premier League by a clear margin. That has seen them plummet into the relegation scrap and while today's fixture cannot be labelled a six-pointer – QPR are surely too far gone for that to be relevant – it is for Stoke a vital opportunity to stop the rot before it is too late. <strong>John Ashdown</strong></p><p><strong>Venue</strong> Loftus Road, Saturday 3pm</p><p><strong>Tickets </strong>£15-35 (08444 777 007)</p><p><strong>Last season </strong>QPR 1 Stoke 0</p><p><strong>Referee </strong>Chris Foy</p><p><strong>This season's matches</strong> 20 <strong>Y</strong>42, <strong>R</strong>12, 2.15 cards per game</p><p><strong>Odds </strong>QPR 6-5 Stoke 5-2 Draw 9-4</p><h2><strong>Queens Park Rangers</strong></h2><p><strong>Subs from</strong> Green, Murphy, Traoré, Yun, Granero, Diakité, Derry, Taarabt, Magri, Bosingwa, Bothroyd, Hoilett</p><p><strong>Doubtful</strong> Traoré (calf)</p><p><strong>Injured</strong> Johnson (knee, 12 May), Campbell (foot, Aug), Wright-Phillips (ankle, Aug)</p><p><strong>Suspended</strong> Zamora (second of three)</p><p><strong>Form guide</strong> LDLLWW</p><p><strong>Disciplinary record</strong> Y51 R3</p><p><strong>Leading scorers </strong>Rémy, Taarabt 5</p><h2><strong>Stoke</strong></h2><p><strong>Subs from</strong> Sorensen, Wilkinson, Shea, Ness, Whitehead, Palacios, Etherington, Kightly, Crouch, Jerome</p><p><strong>Doubtful</strong> Etherington (back), Wilson (hamstring)</p><p><strong>Injured</strong> None</p><p><strong>Suspended</strong> None</p><p><strong>Form guide</strong> LLLDLL</p><p><strong>Disciplinary record</strong> Y67 R3</p><p><strong>Leading scorer</strong> Walters 6</p><h2><strong>Match pointers</strong></h2><p><strong>• Harry Redknapp has won four of his 20 league games in charge of QPR, giving him an identical win ratio (20%) to former managers Mark Hughes and Neil Warnock</strong></p><p></p><p><strong>• If Stoke lose they will equal their worst ever run of seven Premier League away defeats that they set in January – April 2011</strong></p><p></p><p><strong>• QPR have scored the first goal of the game on fewer occasions (nine) than any other side in the division</strong></p><p></p><p><strong>• Stoke have scored (57%) and conceded (46%) the highest percentage of goals from set pieces in the top flight this season</strong></p><p></p><p><strong>• Loïc Rémy is QPR's joint top scorer this season despite playing just nine league games</strong></p><div class=\"related\" style=\"float: left; margin-right: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px;\"><ul><li><a href=\"http://www.guardian.co.uk/football/qpr\">QPR</a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.guardian.co.uk/football/stokecity\">Stoke City</a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.guardian.co.uk/football/premierleague\">Premier League</a></li></ul></div><br/><div class=\"terms\"><a href=\"http://www.guardian.co.uk\">guardian.co.uk</a> &copy; 2013 Guardian News and Media Limited or its affiliated companies. All rights reserved. | Use of this content is subject to our <a href=\"http://www.guardian.co.uk/help/terms-of-service\">Terms & Conditions</a> | <a href=\"http://www.guardian.co.uk/help/feeds\">More Feeds</a></div><p style=\"clear:both\" /><img width='1' height='1' src='http://guardian.co.uk.feedsportal.com/c/34708/f/639039/s/2aeb7887/mf.gif' border='0'/><div class='mf-viral'><table border='0'><tr><td valign='middle'><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.guardian.co.uk%2Ffootball%2F2013%2Fapr%2F19%2Fqpr-stoke-city-squad-sheets&t=Queens+Park+Rangers+v+Stoke+City%3A+squad%C2%A0sheets\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" border=\"0\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.guardian.co.uk%2Ffootball%2F2013%2Fapr%2F19%2Fqpr-stoke-city-squad-sheets&t=Queens+Park+Rangers+v+Stoke+City%3A+squad%C2%A0sheets\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" border=\"0\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.guardian.co.uk%2Ffootball%2F2013%2Fapr%2F19%2Fqpr-stoke-city-squad-sheets&t=Queens+Park+Rangers+v+Stoke+City%3A+squad%C2%A0sheets\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" border=\"0\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%